<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #EF4444; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; }
        .footer { background-color: #333; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; }
        .warning-box { background-color: #FEE2E2; border-left: 4px solid #EF4444; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Return Request Declined</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{customerName}},</p>
            
            <p>We've reviewed your return request (RMA {{rmaNumber}}) and unfortunately, we're unable to approve it at this time.</p>
            
            <div class="warning-box">
                <h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">Reason for Decline:</h3>
                <p style="margin: 0;">{{reason}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>If you believe this decision was made in error or if you have additional information to provide, please contact our customer support team. We're here to help!</p>
            
            <p>Contact us: support@citadelbuy.com</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 CitadelBuy. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
